7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Airtable Automations and Bardeen share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. Where Airtable Automations pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Code Support and Team Collaboration and Webhook Support, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Airtable Automations holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Bardeen scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Airtable Automations and Bardeen offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Airtable Automations's free tier and Bardeen's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
